		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">psycho wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">So, from that, I got that all blocks except the last one would be mapped at $8000, no?</div>
<br />As tepples said, the programmer can choose to map the last bank at $8000 (just like any other bank), in adition to it being already mapped at $c000. I doubt many games, if any, did this. But it's just good to know that it's possible.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
